    <Spell OriginalReference="">
      <Name>Detect Manifest Zone</Name>
      <Schools>
        <School>
          <School>Divination</School>
          <Subschool />
          <Descriptors />
          <Alignments />
          <Properties />
        </School>
      </Schools>
      <CastingTime>1a</CastingTime>
      <Range>Centered</Range>
      <Duration>= "[c] up to " &amp; CasterLevel * 10 &amp; " min (d)"</Duration>
      <Area>120' em. spd</Area>
      <Components>
        <Component>DivineFocus</Component>
        <Component>Somatic</Component>
        <Component>Verbal</Component>
      </Components>
      <MaterialComponentCost>0</MaterialComponentCost>
      <FocusCost>0</FocusCost>
      <XPCost>0</XPCost>
      <Save>None</Save>
      <SaveDCMod>0</SaveDCMod>
      <Page>150</Page>
      <SR>false</SR>
      <Description>You can sense the presence of manifest zones. The amount of information revealed depends on how long you study a particular area or subject. The spell area penetrates barriers, but a thin sheet of lead, 1 in. of common metal, 1 ft of stone, or 3 ft of wood or dirt block it.&#xD;
&#xD;
1st rd) Presence or Absense of manifest zone (if zone is obvious to naked eye, you get no further information on the 1st rd). If zone is in range but not LOS you discern direction but not exact location.&#xD;
2nd rd) Age of manifest zone (see text). If the zone is going to fade within the next 24hrs you learn that as well.&#xD;
3rd rd) The plane connected to the zone. If the zone is small and fits entirely within the area you learn its exact borders and dimensions, otherwise you gain no sense of the precise location.</Description>
    </Spell>
