      <Description>You imbue the target with positive energy which he can then release (in controlled amounts or all at once). You bestow "&amp; Min(30, ( CasterLevel *3)) &amp;" pts of positive energy. The target can expend this energy to heal with a touch, or harm creatures vulnerable to positive energy, removing or dealing 1 pt of dmg. Target also gains a +1 (sacred) on Saves against Necromantic and Death effects until all the bestowed energy has been expended (or the spell ends).</Description>
