      <Duration>Inst.</Duration>
      <Area>5' r.</Area>
      <Components>
        <Component>Material</Component>
        <Component>Visual</Component>
        <Component>XP</Component>
      </Components>
      <MaterialComponentCost>1000</MaterialComponentCost>
      <FocusCost>0</FocusCost>
      <XPCost>750</XPCost>
      <Save>None</Save>
      <SaveDCMod>0</SaveDCMod>
      <Page>152</Page>
      <SR>false</SR>
      <Description>Create a manifest zone of a specified plane, anchored to a specific point prepared for that purpose (such as a quori monolith). The anchorpoint must include a Siberys dragonshard or a piece of material or essence from the anchored plane of at least 1,000gp value.&#xD;
This power works only on the Material Plance, and you must remain within 30ft of the anchor site during the entire manifestation time.  Once created, the fledgeling zone expands its radius at the rate of 5ft per day to a max radius of 150ft. Additional manifestations do not stack (although multiple adjacent or overlapping areas can be created). The new manifest zone has one planar trait of your choice from the plane to which it is connected. The manifest zones can be enhanced using Intensify Manifest Zone or Psionic Intensify Manifest Zone.</Description>
    </Spell>
