      <SR>true</SR>
      <Description>You forge a minor telepathic link with other beings within range, broadcasting soothing thoughts to counteract negative emotions. You can include or exclude from this broadcast any creature you can see, as well as any creature that you know or know of. Creatures affected by this power gain +4 (morale) against Fear effects.&#xD;
At any time during the duration you can choose to trigger its secondary effect. This immediately ends the powers duration, but also instantly removes any Fear effects current affecting the power's targets. It also removes Confused or Fascinated conditions from any of the power's targets.</Description>
    </Spell>
